      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was performed at the nominal operating point (4.5 L/min, 3000 RPM) using mesh counts of 2.1M, 5.8M, and 14.2M cells. GCI for the NIH QoI was 3.2% between the medium and fine meshes, satisfying the acceptance criterion. The fine mesh (14.2M cells) was adopted for all subsequent simulations."
